products.product_name: Online Ballet Sessions with Aashumi Vora
products.product_description: Aashumi Vora is a Dancer. She has received extensive Contemporary and Ballet training at The Danceworx under Ashley Lobo, Ballet Master Yehuda Maor, Yuko Harada and many national and and international faculties. She was also a part of Navdhara India Dance Theatre, a touring artistic Contemporary company, and travelled with them to Turkey for performances. She has been a part of Dance musicals and many live stage shows, events and advertisements. Aashumi has been teaching dance for more than 12 years and loves to share her knowledge and passion with other dance enthusiasts.

products.product_name: Online Football Training with Sporko Football Training School
product_description: Sporko Football Training School is an Academy and a Club based in Mumbai and affiliated to the Mumbai District Football Association. The academy has existing teams under the names of FCI (participating in Super and 1st division of Mumbai District Football Association), CSL and Utkarsh Mandal (participating in 2nd division of Mumbai District Football Association), and Hedgewar Boys (Participating in 3rd division of Mumbai District Football Association).

The academy has been accredited as a WIFA , Mumbai City FC Development Centre and is a part of the AIFF, WIFA, Mumbai City FC Baby League in the under 8,10 and 12 age category under the name Community FCI.
The academy has under-16 team (Hedgewar Boys), that recently won the Mumbai District Football Association Youth League.
All the coaches are AIFF-Licensed and we provide age group specific training.

products.product_name: Online Chess Training by Checkmate Chess Academy
products.product_description: Checkmate Chess Academy is one of the leading chess academies of India. It was founded by FIDE Rated Chess Player Jay Pradhan in 2011 and it is situated in Mumbai, Maharashtra. Checkmate Chess Academy is the highest rated and reviewed academy on Justdial in Chess Category group. We provide customised chess sessions for young kids. We have courses ranging from beginner to advanced level for all age groups. The Academy's client base extends to international regions as well (USA , UK , Germany , France , UAE , Singapore and many more countries) Chess is a fascinating game of intelligence and smartness. It is also beneficial for brain development. The training programmes in our academy are designed to teach students the strategies of chess by making them practice really hard. Our skilled and professional coaches make the whole chess learning a fun learning activity. The kids have won laurels at State , National and International Level as well. We even provide special classes to individuals or educational institutes on special request.
